headline: VMG Health Names Industry Veteran Wes Champion as CEO to Drive Next Era of Growth
summary: DALLAS, January 08, 2026--VMG Health, the leading healthcare consulting firm for business performance, announced today that its board of directors has appointed Wes Champion as Chief Executive Officer. Champion brings more than 35 years of leadership experience in healthcare consulting and technology services to VMG Health as it enters its next phase of innovation and growth.
